Plenty Of Girls In The Sea

version_description: These are the bare-bones chords, nothing fancy. I was really surprised at how easy this was, compared to a lot of MGMT's other work.
Chords are tricky, as usual with MGMT, but I think these are correct.
If you want the simplest chords, transpose up 4 and then place a capo on the 4th fret.
